The paper discusses a new deep learning framework that aims to address challenges faced by AI practitioners in implementation, interpretation, and traceability of state-of-the-art deep learning models. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computer Science related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
